  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class CapacityExceededException
extends RuntimeException
    Indicates that a problem construction or translation task failed because the capacity of the index representation was exceeded.
    Author:
    Emina Torlak
    Specfields:
    dims: IntVector // contains a vector of dimensions which exceed the representation capacity
